ublic</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/696150/extras/9b036dc2c41856647346f60f2281088e.poster.avif?t=1763392465\" width=600 height=34 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/696150/extras/9b036dc2c41856647346f60f2281088e.webm?t=1763392465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/696150/extras/9b036dc2c41856647346f60f2281088e.mp4?t=1763392465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The fame awaits. And you don’t do it for just yourself: you do it for the society. Enter the crazy neon racing world and become the hero of your neighborhood today!</strong>",
